### Artists API Manual Test Collection

@base = http://localhost:3000/api/artists
@auth = Bearer {{token}}

### Crear artista (status interno = PENDING)
POST {{base}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth}}

{
  "artist_name": "Queen",
  "biography": "Legendaria banda británica de rock.",
  "formation_year": 1970,
  "country_code": "GB"
}
###

### Actualizar artista (no cambia status)
PUT {{base}}/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth}}

{
  "biography": "Banda británica de rock formada en 1970 (actualizada)."
}
###

### Aceptar artista (requiere permiso artist.accept)
PUT {{base}}/1/accept
Authorization: {{auth}}
###

### Rechazar artista (requiere permiso artist.reject)
PUT {{base}}/2/reject
Authorization: {{auth}}
###

### Buscar artistas (filtros nombre, país, status)
GET {{base}}?name=Queen
Authorization: {{auth}}
###

### Buscar artistas por país
GET {{base}}?country=GB
Authorization: {{auth}}
###

### Buscar artistas ACTIVE
GET {{base}}?status=ACTIVE
Authorization: {{auth}}
###

### Obtener artista por id
GET {{base}}/1
Authorization: {{auth}}
###

### Borrado lógico de artista (status=DELETED)
DELETE {{base}}/1
Authorization: {{auth}}
###

### Notas
# - status permitido: PENDING|ACTIVE|REJECTED|DELETED (controlado por backend)
# - Transiciones invalidas devuelven 409 BUSINESS_RULE_VIOLATION
# - Permisos requeridos: artist.create, artist.update, artist.delete, artist.accept, artist.reject
